{
  "stem": "9878.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "My sister couldn't make it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She was a strong woman, but she had a little girl on the floor under standing here, a little girl on their arm.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You know, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she couldn't get into the truck, because all the other people kept on pushing.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And needless to say, not a single woman, not a single child, came back.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We find out later and after the war from the farmers in the [NON-ENGLISH], in the area where they kept on doing the killing, that there they dumped them in open graves, the children with them, and their mothers.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "This what I want to bring.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "This is very, very important to bring up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I saw it with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I saw the truck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I saw the truck.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I saw the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I saw the red crosses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Who didn't know?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Red cross, you see [INAUDIBLE] a salvation.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The women are getting milk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Who wouldn't take to get milk for their children when they didn't have milk for so many months, weeks and weeks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Before-- don't forget, from the 24th, 25th of June, till the ghetto, when the ghetto started, there was a lot of incidents.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From this area that I came out and I survived.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Naturally after-- after a few more weeks later, [INAUDIBLE] people came back from the army.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, you see the pictures.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You see a lot of people stay with the army uniforms.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And other people were hidden someplace in other villages.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But in this area that I was, we came back with nine people that I count was alive.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Maybe later on, more, a couple more people came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But you could count them by the fingers.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
